ations global approach in highyield corporate securities and credit shorts in the structured credit market it invests in a wide universe of highly complex distressed downgraded and noninvestment grade structured credit securities including residential mortgagebacked securities commercial mortgagebacked securities cdo  clo and consumer abs the firm employs opportunistic investing and seeks to invest in stressed and deeply distressed situations it typically employs a fundamental and a technical analysis with a bottom up approach to create its investment portfolio the firm conducts inhouse research to make its investments marathon asset management lp was founded in  and is based in new york new york with additional offices in london united kingdom and singapore detailed description one bryant parkth floornew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwmarathonfundcom key executives for marathon asset management lp mr bruce jeffrey richards chief executive officer president comanaging partner and portfolio manager age  mr louis todd hanover comanaging partner chief investment officer and senior portfolio manager age  mr andrew rabinowitz jd cpa partner and chief operating officer age  mr richard keith ronzetti partner global head of investment analysis  asset management and global head of research mr scott schwartz senior managing director and cohead of commercial real estate compensation as of fiscal year  marathon asset management lp key developments marathon asset management lp presents at bloomberg lp inaugural invest new york summit  jun  pm may   marathon asset management lp presents at bloomberg lp inaugural invest new york summit  jun  pm venue bloomberg hq new york new york united states speakers bruce jeffrey richards chief executive officer president comanaging partner and portfolio manager marathon asset management lp presents at th annual investors conference on clos and leveraged loans may  pm may   marathon asset management lp presents at th annual in