he national futures association nfa and is registered with the commodity futures trading commission cftc in the us the financial services authority fsa in the uk and is notice filed as an exempted fund manager with monetary authority of singapore mas in singapore historyedit marathon was formed in january  as marathon asset management llc by managing members bruce richards and louis hanover who have over  years of investment experience in distressed and situational investing in  marathon was reorganized as a delaware limited partnership on august  the firm relocated its headquarters to one bryant park the worlds most environmentally responsible highrise office building and the first building of its size to achieve a top ranked platinum leadership in energy and environmental design leed certification from us green building council usgbc on july   marathon was selected by the us department of the treasury to serve as one of eight firms to manage the legacy securities public private investment program ppip fund marathon asset management is one of the companies accused of threatening to block the european attempt to save greece from defaulting unless they are guaranteed a significant payout in june  blackstone strategic capital holdings managed by blackstone alternative asset management acquired a minority interest in marathon asset management lp referencesedit  a b approximate figure and can include commitments  marathon asset management optimistic on distressed commercial real estate credit opportunities businesswire june    us department of the treasury archived  at the wayback machine july    bryant park tower gets leed platinum certification inhabitant august    marathon asset management takes corporate social responsibility green august    chu ben greek rescue blocked by hedge fund greed the independent london  january  external linksedit marathon asset management v t e hedge funds investment strategy arbitrage  relative value capital structure arbitrage convertib